description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Beginner Whole Body Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Foundation Builder vibe means Strengthen weak points, rebuild, perfect the basics. This is especially good for Those coming back from injury or refining fundamentals. The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join Peter in Siena for this approachable whole body workout. ...
